    @Reference(authors="J.R.M. Hosking, J. R. Wallis, and E. F. Wood",

public class GeneralizedExtremeValueLMMEstimator
extends AbstractLMMEstimator<GeneralizedExtremeValueDistribution>
    Estimate the parameters of a Generalized Extreme Value Distribution, using the methods of L-Moments (LMM). Reference:

    J. R. M. Hosking, J. R. Wallis, and E. F. Wood
    Estimation of the generalized extreme-value distribution by the method of probability-weighted moments.
    Technometrics 27.3

    Since:
    0.6.0
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
